data.question: What is the difference in the z-coordinate between H(2)[N(1)] and H(10)[N(2)] for Zn(SMC)2?

Compare the y-coordinate of H(12)[C(7)] for Zn(SMC)2 and Cd(SMC)2. Which one is higher?
